[{"name":"陳建丞","email":"ccchen@ntut.edu.tw","latestUpdate":"2007-10-01 10:22:09","objective":"本課程在介紹如何運用企業內與員工之有關資源，包括其能力、知識、技術、態度和激勵，以配合企業整體競爭策略與形式。其內容有：人力資源分析、策略及目標、支援性作業之取得、發展及報酬、人力資源的維護。","schedule":"1.　　10/2     課程簡介與學期報告格式介紹\n��　　老師投影片\n2.　　10/9     工作分析\n��　　Dessler: Ch4\n��　　Siddique, C. M. (2004). Job analysis: A strategic human resource management. International Journal of Human Resource Management, 15, 219-244.\n3.　　10/16    招募(一)：簡介與組織吸引力\n��　　Noe: Ch5\n��　　Turban, D. B., Forret, M. L., &amp; Hendrickson, C. L. (1998). Applicant attraction to firms: Influences of organization reputation, job and organizational attributes, and recruiter behaviors. Journal of Vocational Behavior, 52, 24–44.\n4.　　10/23     招募(二) – 影響招募成效的科技因素\n��　　Cober, R.T., Brown, D. J., Levy, P. E., Cober, A. B., &amp; Keeping, L. M. (2003). Organizational Web Sites：Web site content and style as determinants of organizational attraction. International Journal of Selection and Assessment, 11, 158-169.\n��　　Chapman, D. S., Uggerslev, K. L., &amp; Webster, J. (2003). Applicant reactions to face-to-face and technology-mediated interviews: A field investigation. Journal of Applied Psychology, 88, 944-953.\n5.　　10/30    甄選(一) – 簡介；履歷資料\n��　　Noe: Ch6\n��　　Cole, M. S., Field, H. S., &amp; Giles, W. F. (2003). Using recruiter assessments of applicants’ resume content to predict applicant mental ability and Big Five personality dimensions. International Journal of Selection &amp; Assessment, 11, 78-88.\n6.　　11/6     甄選(二) – 人格特質與智商\n��　　Caldwell, D. F., &amp; Burger, J. M. (1998). Personality characteristics of job applicants and success in screening interviews. Personnel Psychology, 51, 119-136.\n��　　Behling, O. (1998). Employee selection: Will intelligence and conscientiousness do the job? Academy of Management Executive, 12, 77-86.\n7.　　11/13    甄選(三) – 面談與印象管理\n��　　Dessler: Ch7\n��　　Tsai, W. C., Chen, C. C., &amp; Chiu, S. F. (2005). Exploring boundaries of the effects of applicant impression